  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="SK">Nov&#xE9; impulzy pre pr&#xE1;cu s postihnut&#xFD;mi de&#x165;mi v Lokichar</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Work with disabled in Lokichar</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="SK">&lt;p&gt;Program Dobrovo&#x13E;n&#xED;ci pre Afriku pon&#xFA;ka mlad&#xFD;m &#x13E;u&#x10F;om zo Slovenska mo&#x17E;nos&#x165; spozna&#x165; projektov&#xFA; pr&#xE1;cu eRka - Dobrej noviny vo v&#xFD;chodnej Afrike a akt&#xED;vne sa zapoji&#x165; do procesov rozvojovej spolupr&#xE1;ce. Dobrovo&#x13E;n&#xED;ci s&#xFA; zaraden&#xED; do konkr&#xE9;tneho projektu, ktor&#xFD; podporuje Dobr&#xE1; novina a po&#x10D;as troch mesiacov pobytu v krajine sa zap&#xE1;jaj&#xFA; do rozli&#x10D;n&#xFD;ch aktiv&#xED;t v projekte. Dobrovo&#x13E;n&#xED;ci tak z&#xED;skavaj&#xFA; jedine&#x10D;n&#xFA; sk&#xFA;senos&#x165; &#x17E;ivota a pr&#xE1;ce so znev&#xFD;hodnen&#xFD;mi skupinami v novej kult&#xFA;re a lep&#x161;ie rozumej&#xFA; glob&#xE1;lnym t&#xE9;mam a probl&#xE9;mom.&lt;/p&gt;</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&lt;p&gt;Volunteers for Africa program offers young people the opportunity to learn from Slovak project named eRko - Good news in East Africa and actively engage in the processes of development cooperation. Volunteers are assigned to a particular project, which supports the Good News, and within three months of residence in the country are engaged in different activities in the project. Volunteers thus gain an unique experience of living and working with disadvantaged groups in the new culture and a better understanding of global issues and problems.&lt;/p&gt;</narrative>
  </description>
